title: The War on Trans People: Part 5, How the Nazis Destroyed German Queerness
itunes:title: The War on Trans People: Part 5, How the Nazis Destroyed German Queerness
description:
In part 5 the crew heads back in time to look at the development of the original gay rights movement in Germany and how it was destroyed by the Nazis.
